FAQ_SUBTITLE_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: Got questions about our food app? We've got answers!
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_1: What is this food app all about?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_1: Our app is your ultimate food companion, offering recipe ideas, restaurant recommendations, and meal planning tools all in one place.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_2: Is the app free to use?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_2: Yes, our basic features are free. We also offer a premium version with additional perks for food enthusiasts.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_3: Can I use the app to order food?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_3: Absolutely! We've partnered with local restaurants to offer seamless food ordering and delivery right from the app.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_4: How do I create a personalized meal plan?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_4: Simply input your dietary preferences and goals, and our app will generate a custom meal plan tailored just for you.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_5: Are the recipes suitable for beginners?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_5: Yes! We offer recipes for all skill levels, from novice cooks to seasoned chefs, with step-by-step instructions and video tutorials.
PLACEHOLDER_FAQ_TITLE: Frequently Asked Questions About Our Food App
ACCORDION_QUESTION_1: How does the food app work?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_1: Our food app allows you to browse local restaurants, view menus, place orders, and track deliveries all in one place. Simply download the app, create an account, and start exploring delicious options in your area.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_2: Is there a minimum order amount?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_2: Minimum order amounts may vary depending on the restaurant and your location. You can easily see any minimum order requirements when browsing restaurant menus within the app.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_3: How can I track my food delivery?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_3: Once your order is confirmed, you can track its progress in real-time through the app. You'll receive notifications for order confirmation, preparation, and when your delivery driver is on the way.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_4: Are there any fees for using the app?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_4: The app is free to download and use. However, there may be delivery fees, service charges, or small order fees depending on the restaurant and your order details. All applicable fees will be clearly displayed before you complete your order.
